	<dl>
	<dt>A single vote makes no difference to...</dt>
	<dd><p>A single vote makes no difference to the overall outcome, or to the outcome in my local constituency. I have heard constantly the retort "well, if everyone thought like that..., etc" - but whether or not I choose to vote will have no bearing on whether any other person chooses to. I do not try to persuade other people not to vote, they should do as they please but I shall not be voting as there is no point, my vote will not make a difference.</p>
	<small>
	written 14th Apr 2005 <!--  | <a href="../email/784">Email this
    to a friend</a> | <a
    href="/abuse/?postid=784">abusive?</a> -->
	</small>
	</dd>
	</dl>

